Class WeightedEdge

All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable
public class WeightedEdge extends org.jgrapht.graph.DefaultEdge
The WeightedEdge class represents an edge in a graph with an associated weight. It extends the DefaultEdge class from the JGraphT library, allowing it to store additional data, such as the weight of the edge.

Weights are typically used to represent the strength, cost, or percentage associated with the edge in the graph.
